      "title": "My latest New Scientist cartoon",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s640x960/c4ae228287ab55d2b6543ffb60db2310642e8880.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"988\" data-orig-width=\"1400\" alt=\" Image: A scientist proudly shows an extremely complicated machine to a colleague &quot;My experiment is generating infinite power!&quot;. A screen displays the infinity symbol &quot;&#xE2;&#x88;&#x9E;&quot; and a label reading &quot;watts&quot;  Caption: Simon assumed that Veronica was speechless with envy and awe, but she was actually wondering how to break it to him that the monitor was on its side. \" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s75x75_c1/9fce4dd1e92bbeb8b6f1037e0e3f7f9c8f77969c.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s100x200/d5fc22160056acc73bd86850a993eaaf45e7e58e.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s250x400/3295fca3554209a84a8624db5d3535011a403cb0.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s400x600/fe1c78e14bd1e98f8bdfb9ea03262c28ea5eb6bf.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s500x750/0fa4c2da1749aabef1f4c09f0ce2261015e48cbc.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s540x810/b39730ad72c96b7703d207d9a9610bf50dc09c49.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s640x960/c4ae228287ab55d2b6543ffb60db2310642e8880.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s1280x1920/0fa1b2e644dae6c4cb6288ff8e686516246118df.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/4bb6eb091db3c2b0fe8f6f31b8259971/9a7648b32b81d1ad-80/s2048x3072/f337de633fad10d720c738ae9e5e099df2f311ed.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
